cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "SmartSepsis-Oph: AI-first molecular diagnostics design for ophthalmic infections"
message: "If you use this software or its design outputs, please cite as below."
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: João Victor
    family-names: Pacheco Dias
    affiliation: "IA para Médicos / HC-FMUSP (doctoral candidate)"
    orcid: ""
